1
00:00:36,210 --> 00:00:40,940
[Story of Nangong]

2
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:52,930
Cheng, what wish did you make today?

3
00:00:52,950 --> 00:00:53,950
I hope

4
00:00:53,980 --> 00:00:57,500
Father, Mother, and I will be together forever.

5
00:00:58,380 --> 00:00:59,840
Mother!

6
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:01,710
Cheng!

7
00:01:02,780 --> 00:01:04,540
Mother!

8
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:08,070
Mother!

9
00:01:12,100 --> 00:01:17,750
♫Lovesickness lingers at my fingertips, rouge-stained lips lightly bitten♫

10
00:01:18,789 --> 00:01:24,950
♫Wind twines dark tresses, misty rain stirs, who is laughing?♫

11
00:01:21,550 --> 00:01:23,110
Mother, don't go.

12
00:01:23,140 --> 00:01:25,490
I won't let you leave.

13
00:01:25,510 --> 00:01:28,110
Please don't go.

14
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:29,100
♫I only regret we didn't meet earlier♫

15
00:01:28,140 --> 00:01:30,020
Please!

16
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,120
Mother!

17
00:01:30,550 --> 00:01:32,700
♫While we're still young♫

18
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,110
Cheng!

19
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:33,280
Cheng!

20
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:38,350
♫Let me play a lovesick melody with you again♫

21
00:01:35,370 --> 00:01:37,100
Mother!

22
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,400
Cheng!

23
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,759
Mother!

24
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:43,539
Where are you going?

25
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:47,850
Where is Cheng?

26
00:01:48,210 --> 00:01:49,330
I want to see him.

27
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,520
What's the hurry?

28
00:01:52,910 --> 00:01:54,460
Just focus on your task.

29
00:01:54,539 --> 00:01:55,660
You and your son

30
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,130
will meet in due time.

31
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:06,710
[We should divorce]

32
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:06,710
[Episode 11]

33
00:02:14,510 --> 00:02:15,590
Li Luo!

34
00:02:20,020 --> 00:02:20,880
Your Highness.

35
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:21,910
Li Luo,

36
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,420
why am I here?

37
00:02:23,810 --> 00:02:24,760
Your Highness,

38
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:27,160
Nangong Ying...

39
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:32,070
Nangong Ying, you bitch!

40
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:33,930
When I become the empress,

41
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,329
I'll teach you a lesson.

42
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:24,850
Your Majesty, no need to waste your efforts.

43
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:28,410
I just don't want her to see you like this

44
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,440
and feel troubled.

45
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:37,180
If you hadn't taken her from me,

46
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,750
we wouldn't have been separated!

47
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:42,480
You are the emperor,

48
00:03:43,050 --> 00:03:45,750
but I will not yield so easily!

49
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:48,630
You've been with Ying for five years,

50
00:03:49,550 --> 00:03:51,750
yet you don't understand her at all.

51
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,750
She may appear gentle and obedient,

52
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:56,460
but actually, she is wise and resolute.

53
00:03:56,730 --> 00:03:58,740
If she doesn't want to divorce,

54
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:00,140
even I

55
00:04:00,210 --> 00:04:01,790
can't force her to do so.

56
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:03,920
Let go.

57
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:07,320
Don't make her suffer anymore.

58
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:09,970
You...

59
00:04:10,370 --> 00:04:11,410
You...

60
00:04:11,790 --> 00:04:13,430
Nonsense!

61
00:04:16,820 --> 00:04:18,000
Your Majesty, I, Pei Ming,

62
00:04:18,029 --> 00:04:19,339
pay my respects to you.

63
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:21,570
Your Majesty,

64
00:04:21,709 --> 00:04:23,740
I have failed to discipline my son properly,

65
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:25,430
but Your Majesty, please be clear.

66
00:04:25,490 --> 00:04:30,260
No matter what, he would never dare deceive or defy you.

67
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,940
The Pei family has served the court for three generations

68
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,570
and is a pillar of the country.

69
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:44,890
Of course I believe the Pei family would never defy an imperial decree

70
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,500
or commit treason.

71
00:04:47,710 --> 00:04:49,650
It's just that Young General Pei

72
00:04:50,050 --> 00:04:53,350
is deeply in love with Nangong Ying.

73
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:55,640
You bastard.

74
00:04:55,659 --> 00:04:56,980
Do you want to get Cheng

75
00:04:57,010 --> 00:04:58,570
and the general's household into trouble?

76
00:04:58,590 --> 00:04:59,790
Just accept the imperial decree

77
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:01,260
and write the divorce letter!

78
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:08,550
♫A thousand sails have passed, spanning the ages♫

79
00:05:03,490 --> 00:05:04,370
Father!

80
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:06,820
Ying is my wife.

81
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:09,660
His Majesty took her from me.

82
00:05:09,810 --> 00:05:12,040
That's why we've been separated!

83
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:15,270
♫The lone swan cries out in sorrow♫

84
00:05:12,450 --> 00:05:14,170
Shut up!

85
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:23,800
♫This fleeting life suddenly reaches dusk♫

86
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,260
I'll write it.

87
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:30,020
♫The evening wind brings snow, and the boat won't cross♫

88
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,920
Xian.

89
00:05:27,410 --> 00:05:29,100
[Hanzhang Hall]

90
00:05:28,590 --> 00:05:29,710
I'm sorry.

91
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:32,490
What I want to do is too dangerous.

92
00:05:31,290 --> 00:05:37,300
♫Peach blossoms fall where I sleep soundly, and the moon remains unchanged♫

93
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:34,420
I can't get you implicated.

94
00:05:35,260 --> 00:05:37,120
All marriages are the results

95
00:05:37,150 --> 00:05:39,280
of bonds formed over three lifetimes,

96
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:44,880
♫In the night rain, we talk softly over a jug of wine♫

97
00:05:39,490 --> 00:05:41,710
destined to unite souls in this one.

98
00:05:42,290 --> 00:05:44,110
But now, our hearts have drifted apart,

99
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,990
and we are no longer of one mind.

100
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,710
Let us each walk our own path.

101
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:48,830
♫No way back, no looking back♫

102
00:05:48,850 --> 00:05:51,060
After we part ways, I hope

103
00:05:50,330 --> 00:05:53,550
♫Even beautiful scenes pass in vain♫

104
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:53,180
you can find your true love in this life.

105
00:05:53,210 --> 00:05:54,820
When we meet again,

106
00:05:54,850 --> 00:05:57,270
I will have forgotten the past with no regrets.

107
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:59,470
♫Trapped in dawn and dusk♫

108
00:06:00,470 --> 00:06:01,520
Xian.

109
00:06:00,590 --> 00:06:06,780
♫The candle by the west window burns out, this life ends in emptiness♫

110
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:03,000
Let go.

111
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:05,630
This is good for both of us.

112
00:06:06,290 --> 00:06:08,070
Don't be so stubborn anymore.

113
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:14,380
♫Why yearn for the absent one through changing seasons♫

114
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:12,290
I'm not being stubborn,

115
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:23,480
♫A cup of earth, a long shot gamble, a sigh of late life♫

116
00:06:15,540 --> 00:06:16,940
I just don't understand.

117
00:06:20,210 --> 00:06:21,850
Even if I die,

118
00:06:22,610 --> 00:06:25,900
I want to die as your husband.

119
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:29,890
♫No one to accompany♫

120
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:37,360
♫The candle by the west window burns out, this life ends in emptiness♫

121
00:06:31,150 --> 00:06:32,650
But I don't want that.

122
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:36,450
I don't want to stay by His Majesty's side

123
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:38,070
as Pei Xian's wife.

124
00:06:38,450 --> 00:06:44,470
♫Why yearn for the absent one through changing seasons♫

125
00:06:45,940 --> 00:06:52,650
♫A cup of earth, a long shot gamble, a sigh of late life♫

126
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:48,220
Alright.

127
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:50,430
From today on,

128
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,500
Nangong Ying and Pei Xian

129
00:06:52,530 --> 00:06:53,860
will have nothing to do with each other.

130
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,610
From now on,

131
00:06:54,990 --> 00:07:01,040
♫No one to accompany♫

132
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,960
their marriages will be

133
00:06:56,990 --> 00:06:58,140
none of each other's concern.

134
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:09,630
[Nangong Ying][Pei Xian]

135
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:17,470
What?

136
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:19,380
You don't want to divorce

137
00:07:19,410 --> 00:07:20,480
Young General?

138
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:22,150
Your Majesty, please don't misunderstand.

139
00:07:22,570 --> 00:07:23,730
I can...

140
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:26,570
be with you without guilt from now on, right?

141
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,520
Be with me?

142
00:07:28,650 --> 00:07:29,990
You put knockout drops in my wine.

143
00:07:30,020 --> 00:07:31,700
Was that also to be with me?

144
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,200
I did that because I was worried

145
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:36,990
you wouldn't let me go back to General's Mansion.

146
00:07:38,909 --> 00:07:41,010
You've become increasingly capable.

147
00:07:43,210 --> 00:07:43,930
Master,

148
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:45,870
this is the roster of the Pei family.

149
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,590
You were right.

150
00:07:47,980 --> 00:07:49,740
They've indeed raised quite a few private soldiers.

151
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:58,310
Master,

152
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,230
you can rest assured now.

153
00:08:00,890 --> 00:08:02,450
Whatever the Pei family does,

154
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:05,020
Ms. Nangong won't be implicated.

155
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:19,030
Xian,

156
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:20,420
I'm sorry.

157
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:22,610
I can't get you implicated anymore.

158
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,930
I hope you won't do anything stupid again.
